OL,5, British Gas owner Centrica has resumed 
OL,6, payouts to shareholders as UK          
OL,7, households come under pressure from    
OL,8, rising energy bills.                   
OL,10,FThe company said it was paying an      
OL,11,Finterim dividend of 1p per share, after
OL,12,Fhaving suspended it for three years.   
OL,14,FIt comes as gas prices soar, fuelled by
OL,15,FRussia's war in Ukraine.               
OL,17,FUK energy bills are expected to rise   
OL,18,Fagain in the coming months, with one   
OL,19,Fconsultancy warning they could hit     
OL,20,F#3,850 a year by January.              
